description:
A new way to collaborate

Empowering teams by messenger, meetings, calendar, docs, and emails. It's all in one place.
System and version
- The Feishu mobile app is now compatible with HarmonyOS Next. If you have upgraded to HarmonyOS 5.0 or above, you can download and install Feishu directly from the app gallery. We’ll continue to enhance Feishu’s features for HarmonyOS users, so stay tuned for future updates.
